title: Guardians Of The Video Game
description:
Description :
        From LINE Webtoon: Patch is an elite agent working for a secret company that builds, operates, and guards the world of video game unbeknownst to game players. His perfect career as an elite agent starts to crumble as he gets sighted by a game player on site...
